OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe men risking their lives
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto be Catholic priests     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, When Miguel Pantaleon was ordained into
OL,6, the Catholic church last month, it was 
OL,7, the biggest day of his young life.     
OL,9,FThe 28-year-old trainee priest had     
OL,10,Fspent almost a decade working towards  
OL,11,Fjoining the clergy. At a packed mass in
OL,12,Fhis dusty village of Rincon del Carmen 
OL,13,Fin western Mexico, he was officially   
OL,14,Fbrought into the priesthood by the     
OL,15,Fdiocese bishop.                        
OL,17,FWatching in the front pew, his mother, 
OL,18,FPetra Florencio, beamed with pride.    
OL,19,FMiguel is the 11th of 13 children, and 
OL,20,Fhis vocation is a source of great      
OL,21,Fprestige for his family.               
